take good care of yourself.

126
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,920
Besides...

127
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,720
Besides, I wanted to see you.

128
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,160
Since you said that,

129
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,360
