151
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,800
Of course.

152
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,959
I'm not good at this.

153
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,959
There's no one that I can't teach.

154
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,120
