264
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:07,130
- I am not...
- Mr. He.

265
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,639
What you said just now

266
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:10,960
was a fallacy of composition.

267
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:13,240
I can vouch on my honor

268
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:16,000
